---
---
<section class="reveal relative py-[52.8px] bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
    <img src="/images/BG-2-1.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[1340px] w-full mx-auto px-[10px] relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] items-center gap-4">
          <div class="mx-auto">
            <img src="/images/process/Step-1-1.png" alt="Consultation" class="w-[96px] h-[96px] object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mb-2">Consultation: Listen, Learn, Deliver</h4>
            <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#757575]">We take the time to listen and understand your needs, learning about your brand identity and goals. Our collaborative approach ensures we design sportswear that meets your expectations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] items-center gap-4">
          <div class="mx-auto">
            <img src="/images/Icon-1-1.png" alt="Concept" class="w-[96px] h-[96px] object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mb-2">Concept: Design with Precision</h4>
            <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#757575]">Our experienced designers meticulously craft custom sportswear designs, incorporating your feedback to achieve perfection.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] items-center gap-4">
          <div class="mx-auto">
            <img src="/images/process/Step-2-1.png" alt="Production" class="w-[96px] h-[96px] object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mb-2">Production: Uncompromising Quality</h4>
            <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#757575]">Our skilled workers pay attention to every detail, using high-quality materials and precise techniques to produce sportswear that reflects excellence and craftsmanship.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[120px_1fr] items-center gap-4">
          <div class="mx-auto">
            <img src="/images/Service-6-1.png" alt="Delivery" class="w-[96px] h-[96px] object-contain" />
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mb-2">The Final Result: Timely Delivery</h4>
            <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#757575]">We prioritize meeting your deadlines, ensuring that your sportswear is delivered on time and ready to make an impact.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-nav text-[19.2px] font-semibold tracking-[2.5px] text-[#A6587C] uppercase mb-3">HOW WE WORK</h2>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[52.8px] font-semibold leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mb-4">Find The Fabric, Enjoy The Process and The Results</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#757575] mb-4">At ICM Factory Direct, our work ethics revolve around understanding your needs and delivering exceptional results. Choose ICM Factory Direct for a collaborative approach that prioritizes understanding your needs, designing to perfection, producing sportswear with meticulous attention to detail, and delivering the final result on time.</p>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#757575] mb-8">We are committed to creating sportswear that embodies your brand's identity and exceeds your expectations at every step of the process.</p>
        <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#A6587C] hover:bg-[#7D405C] text-[#F4F4F4] font-nav text-[14.4px] leading-[1] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase py-[15px] px-[36px] transition-colors duration-300">
          NEED HELP
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
